pygame.Mask
pygame object for representing 2d bitmasks
pygame.Mask((width, height): return Mask

Useful for fast pixel perfect collision detection.  A Mask uses 1bit per 
pixel to store which parts collide.

New in pygame 1.8.

<SECTION>

